docs.text: 2048小程序一键部署 部署流程 访问计算巢2048小程序 部署链接 ，按提示填写部署参数： 参数填写完成后可以看到对应询价明细，确认参数后点击 下一步：确认订单 。 确认订单完成后同意服务协议并点击 立即创建 进入部署阶段。 等待部署完成后就可以开始使用服务，进入服务实例详情点击服务地址。

docs.text: 2048 applet one-click deployment Deployment process Visit the calculation nest 2048 applet deployment link and fill in the deployment parameters as prompted: After completing the parameters, you can see the corresponding RFQ details. After confirming the parameters, click Next: Confirm Order . Confirm that the order is complete and agree to the service agreement and click Create Now to enter the deployment phase. After the deployment is completed, you can start using the service. Enter the service instance details and click the service address.
